working on tags and the ansible vault

tags: these are used to run a specific task or part of task which are inside the playbook
commands:
---------
1) ansible all -m ping --tags dev
2) 1) ansible all -m ping --tags 'dev,stage'
3) ansible all -m ping --list-tags
4) ansible all -m ping --skip-tags dev
5) ansible all -m ping --skip-tags 'dev,stage'



ansible vault: it is used to store the sensitive data by encrypting it
---------------
    open a file 
    vi /etc/ansible/group_vars/all.yml

    enter this value in all.yaml
    ----------------------------
    passoword: 12345

    cmd: ansible-vault encrypt /etc/ansible/group_vars/all.yml   -> when execute this cmd we have to set passoword for the 

    ansible-vault --help
    ansible-vault view file
    ansible-vault edit file
    ansible-vault decrypt file
    



